<P>&startq;My lovely friend&endq;</P>
<P>&startq;La! how pretty!&endq; &s;aid Mi&s;s Dennel; &startq;let's go a
little nearer.&endq;</P>
<P>They advanced, and pre&s;ently, again &s;topping, heard,
&startq;Could pity pour balm into my woes, how &s;weetly
would they be alleviated by your$s my lovely friend?</P>
<P>Mi&s;s Dennel now looked enchanted, and eagerly led
