&s;truck by a piercing &s;hriek.</P>
<P>&startq;O Lord! we &s;hall be murdered!&endq; cried &s;he, &s;cream|ing
&s;till louder her&s;elf.</P>
<P>They both ran back &s;ome paces down the lane, Ca|milla
