mercifully come to my re&s;cue!&endq;</P>
<P>The pur&s;uer drew back and Camilla, in the gentle&s;t
words, be&s;ought the la$y to accompany her to the
friends &s;he had ju&s;t left, who would be happy to protect
her.</P>
<P>She gratefully accepted the propo&s;$$l, and Camilla
then ventured to look round&punc; to &s;ee if the object of this
