as well as from the impo&s;&s;ibility of her knowing that her
<PB N="93" REF="94">
&s;cream could be heard: yet was perplexed how to ac|count
for her not naming her&s;elf, and for the my&s;tery of
the carriage and &s;ervant in waiting &s;o far off The&s;e
latter &s;he concluded to belong to her father, as &s;he
looked too young to have any &s;ort of e&s;tabli&s;hment of
