alone in the &s;hop with Sir Theophilus Jarard, &s;he
&s;aid, &startq;Pray, Sir Theophilus, do you know any thing
of that queer woman?&endq;</P>
<P>The words <HI>queer woman</HI> were guides &s;ufficient to Sir
Theophilus, who an&s;wered, &startq;No! I have &s;een her,
<PB N="120" REF="121">
&s;omewhere, by accident, but&mdash;&s;he is quite out of our
