<P>&startq;When will you introduce me to your new friend,
Mi&s;s Tyrold?&endq; &s;aid Mrs. Arlbery; &startq;or, rather,&endq; (turn|ing
<PB N="126" REF="127">
to Lord Newford,) &startq;I hope your lord&s;hip will do
